‘‘Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ sannayhitvā viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati. So tasmiṃ saṅgāme ussahati  vāyamati. Tamenaṃ ussahantaṃ vāyamantaṃ pare upalikkhantiupalikhanti 
